### Phase 3: Edge Cost 設計（確保 A* 選對路線）

#### [MODIFY] [PathPlanningTracker.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs) — [BuildNavigationGraph()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#602-727)

```csharp
// Edge Cost 策略：
// Walk:      歐幾里得距離 × 1.0 (基準)
// ClimbUp:   固定 5.0  (爬繩快但需對齊)
// ClimbDown: 固定 3.0  (下爬更快)
// Jump:      固定 8.0  (跳躍有風險但節省大量走路)
// JumpDown:  固定 2.0  (下跳最快)

float cost = edge.ActionType switch
{
    NavigationActionType.Walk      => EuclideanDistance(from, to),
    NavigationActionType.ClimbUp   => 5.0f,
    NavigationActionType.ClimbDown => 3.0f,
    NavigationActionType.JumpLeft  => 8.0f,
    NavigationActionType.JumpRight => 8.0f,
    NavigationActionType.JumpDown  => 2.0f,
    _ => EuclideanDistance(from, to)
};
```

> [!NOTE]
> Cost 數值需要根據遊戲實際移動速度微調。上述為初始估計。

---

### Phase 4: 巡邏策略（選擇 A* 終點）

#### [MODIFY] [PathPlanningTracker.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs) — [SelectNextTarget()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1413-1758)

```csharp
// 策略：隨機選擇一個「遠處」的節點做為巡邏目標
// 到達後再選下一個，形成巡邏迴圈
private string SelectPatrolTarget(string currentNodeId)
{
    var allNodes = _navGraph.GetAllNodes().ToList();
    var currentNode = _navGraph.GetNode(currentNodeId);
    
    // 選擇距離最遠的前 3 個節點中隨機一個（增加擬人性）
    var candidates = allNodes
        .Where(n => n.Id != currentNodeId)
        .OrderByDescending(n => Distance(n.Position, currentNode.Position))
        .Take(3)
        .ToList();
    
    return candidates[_random.Next(candidates.Count)].Id;
}
```

